\begin_inset Formula $s={\textstyle \frac{1}{2}}$
\end_inset

 (fermions).
 Each particle carries different charges.
 These determine if it can participate in electromagnetic (EM), in weak
 or in strong interactions.
 The interactions themselves are mediated by bosonic elementary particle
 with spin 
\begin_inset Formula $s=1$
\end_inset

 and are listed in Table 
